                RELEASE  NOTES             
                                                        
                                                          
                                                          
                                                 
                                                    
                                                          
                                                              
                                                                    
                                                                      
                                                                      
                                                                          
                                                                        
                                                                          
                                                                            
             priPrinter is a fast, small, user-friendly virtual               
             printer, previewer, and editor. It has a nice array              
             of features for preview your print jobs. Of course               
             you can print booklets, posters or just put a lot of             
             pages on the one physical paper sheet.                           
                                                                              
             Print document from your application to priPrinter               
             in order to preview it, modify it, print it. Even                
             programs with built in preview can't guarantee exact             
             results. Our mission is to provide perfect print                 
             preview solution, save your paper, printer's ink or              
             toner. With priPrinter you always can be sure how                
             your print will look. Printing comes naturally when              
             you're using priPrinter.                                         
                                                                              
             * 3D Preview                                                     
             * Provides every feature you need to make your print             
               easy and simple.                                               
             * Preview your printing in many ways. Explore                    
               content of your jobs.                                          
             * Print to images. You may save your prints to                   
               various image formats.                                         
             * Booklet and posters.                                           
             * Duplex printing.                                               
             * Measurements.                                                  
             * Print themes                                                   
             * Loupe tool.                                                    
             * Margins and gutters. Change margins and gutters                
               with mouse click and drag.                                     
             * Crop and Cut. Remove blank space and redundant                 
               information.                                                   
             * Undo/Redo                                                      
             * Small and fast.                                                
             * Save jobs to file.                                             
             * Tray control.                                                  
             * There are more features to explore.

             1. Unpack and install.                                           
             2. Import the included registry file.                            
             3. Copy the included files into the installed folder.            
                                                                              
             That's all. Have fun using it! ;-)
